001package edu.cnm.deepdive.passphrase.service;
002
003import edu.cnm.deepdive.passphrase.model.Passphrase;
004import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Completable;
005import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
006import java.util.List;
007import retrofit2.http.Body;
008import retrofit2.http.DELETE;
009import retrofit2.http.GET;
010import retrofit2.http.Header;
011import retrofit2.http.Headers;
012import retrofit2.http.PATCH;
013import retrofit2.http.POST;
014import retrofit2.http.PUT;
015import retrofit2.http.Path;
016import retrofit2.http.Query;
017
018public interface PassphraseServiceProxy {
019
020  @GET("passphrases/{key}")
021  Single<Passphrase> get(@Path("key") String key, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
022
023  @GET("passphrases")
024  Single<List<Passphrase>> get(@Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
025
026  @GET("passphrases")
027  Single<List<Passphrase>> search(@Query("q") String fragment, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
028      
029  @POST("passphrases")
030  Single<Passphrase> post(@Body Passphrase passphrase, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
031
032  @DELETE("passphrases/{key}")
033  Completable delete(@Path("key") String key, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
034
035  @Headers({"Content-Type: application/merge-patch+json"})
036  @PATCH("passphrases/{key}")
037  Single<Passphrase> patch(@Path("key") String key, @Body Passphrase passphrase, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
038
039  @PUT("passphrases/{key}/name")
040  Single<String> put(@Path("key") String key, @Body String name, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
041
042  @PUT("passphrases/{key}/words")
043  Single<List<String>> put(@Path("key") String key, @Body List<String> words, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
044
045  @POST("passphrases/generate")
046  Single<List<String>> generate(@Query("length") int length, @Header("Authorization") String bearerToken);
047
048}
